        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         You can fear kite at entrance, or for even better exp you can kill the Shadowknight version of the Centi Dators Deep in like I do... Go in AR... go straight then right... go straight until you get to the big ruin thing with a centi in front of it... go all the way back there, no agro from the centi in front of the ruin. Load:</P><P>Vex<BR>ToN<BR>Splurt<BR>Pyro<BR>Root of your choice<BR>HS<BR>AL<BR>FD</P><P>Pull the one in front of the ruin, root, dot.. proceed to the one in the middle of the big room, always pull to behind the ruin. There are 2 more to your left, 2 more to your right, static pops, watch for the transient patroller roamers, Keep the whole room clear not counting the 2 lighter skinned centis there are toward the stairs opposite to you.</P><P>NOTE: This is very easy for me because I have my epic... so I barely use any mana, I also suggest you get the extended affliction 3 bracer before doing this camp, it is essential.</P><P>NOTE: This camp is especially nice because you NEVER get Harmtouched... they will always be OOR or out of line of sight.</P><P>NOTE: Repop is I beleive 25 minutes, not sure... 6 centis in 25 minutes... may sound odd but this is actually VERY nice exp because they're considerably higher level than the warriors in the ZI and beyond.</P><P><BR>Hope this helps out...</P><P><font size=5><font color=red><b><center>Zeto</font id=red></b></center></font id=size5><BR><center>-Tholuxe Paells-</center><BR><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125378" target="_blank">My Gear</a></center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
